ygData.subject: Re: Dagnor's Cauldron
ygData.msgSnippet: The entrance to Kedge Keep is somewhere in the zone. About level 30+ entry required I hear. I go straight to Unrest ( undead dungeon ) from the cauldron.
ygData.messageBody:
The entrance to Kedge Keep is somewhere in the zone.
About level 30+ entry required I hear.

I go straight to Unrest ( undead dungeon ) from the
cauldron.

Belgarth Wolfstrider
